---
---
<section id="services" style="padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md); max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">
    <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-4xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Strategic <span class="text-accent">Capabilities.</span></h2>
    <p style="margin: 0 auto; max-width: 50ch;">We design autonomous systems that obliterate friction, targeting compounding efficiencies and exponential outreach.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="asymmetric-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));">
    
    <div class="glass-container animate-fade-in delay-100">
      <div style="font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); font-size: var(--text-2xl);">01</div>
      <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl);">Cloud-Based AI Systems</h3>
      <p style="font-size: var(--text-base);">
        Architecting robust, production-grade applications that seamlessly interface with core business logic. Our automated implementations have directly driven multi-million dollar contract cost savings for key agency clients.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="glass-container animate-fade-in delay-300" style="background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.05);">
      <div style="font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); font-size: var(--text-2xl);">02</div>
      <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl);">Automated Outreach Infrastructure</h3>
      <p style="font-size: var(--text-base);">
        We build intelligent, AI-driven personalization engines that transform cold leads into warm pipeline. Expect mathematically predictable pipeline growth exceeding 300% through highly tuned autonomous engagement.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="glass-container animate-fade-in delay-500">
      <div style="font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); font-size: var(--text-2xl);">03</div>
      <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl);">Agent-Based Workflows</h3>
      <p style="font-size: var(--text-base);">
        Specializing in multi-agent orchestration to compile, synthesize, and produce executive-ready deliverables with strictly zero administrative oversight. The work finishes before you realize it started.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
